There is no vol. 4! This isn't netorare! Read below to understand.

Volume/order: The story in the douj is being published in a comic with other douj. The volume number is for the comic, not the "episode" of the doujin itself. So there was a COMIC GEE Vol 4, but Saimin Seikatsu wasn't in that volume. Just read them in increasing volume order without fear you're missing anything. At time of writing, there's also no Volume 8.

Netorare: Hypnotism supersedes netorare, however the fetish really skirts a line in this douj because one of the characters ebbs into and out of her trance. I think the vast majority of people who have a problem with netorare would be okay with how it's used in this douj, so unless you're in like the top 5% of netorare sensitivity, feel free to read it anyway.
